Understandable to see why it may have been good on Rek'sai, with the Q enhancing your next 3 auto attacks. I do however believe the real reason is because sword of divine was rarely bought on anyone, by anyone, which is a shame because I personally loved Sword of Divine. 

This same scenario applies to Atmas Impaler as well, just never bought.

Same with Fort Pot, I'll miss the days of Fort Pot top.{{item:2037}} {{item:3070}}
